Dev tools

Develop and deploy, your way

Streamline and speed up your work with powerful development tools. Easily integrate with our REST and GraphQL APIs, SDKs and webhooks.

Wix Blocks

Build apps on Wix Blocks, our native app builder. Use familiar tools like drag & drop elements, Velo code and Wix APIs to develop custom features that extend the functionality of Wix’s business solutions.

Go to Wix Blocks docs

Wix CLI

Streamline your app development process with the Wix CLI. Get a familiar developer experience with minimal setup and configuration—and seamlessly integrate your app into Wix Studio.

Go to CLI docs

Self-hosting

Take full control over your app's tech stack, deployment, and hosting. Develop and deploy your app using any tech stack you like. Choose your own tools and libraries, code in any environment, and easily integrate with Wix Studio using the Wix Dev Center.

Go to self-hosting docs
